
question
Write a function called oppositeSum that takes three numbers a, b, c as 
arguments and returns the sum of these numbers with the opposite sign.

Example:

function oppositeSum (1, 2, 3) should return -6;
function oppositeSum (-1, -2, -3) should return 6;

solution:

function oppositeSum(a, b, c){
 let sum = a + b + c;
   if(sum > 0 || sum < 0) return (-sum);
     else if ( a === 0) return 0;
  }
   
